examples.en: With the proper conditioning, the horse will learn to trust and obey its handler.
Social conditioning makes crying more difficult for men.
The air conditioning was broken, and it was sweltering in the office.
Conditioning is a form of learning by association.
The air conditioning doesn't seem to be cooling the room much.
I could freeze to death in this office when the air conditioning is turned on.
The office was broiling because the air conditioning was on the blink.
